	<article class='post' id="post-556072" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">

		<h1 id="headline" itemprop="url headline name">Bitcoin Survival Guide: Everything You Need to Know About the Future of Money</h1>
<link itemprop="url" href="http://www.wired.com/2013/11/bitcoin-survival-guide/" />
<link itemprop="image" href="http://www.wired.com/wp-content/uploads/images_blogs/wiredenterprise/2013/11/bitcoin-illo.jpg" />

<ul class="entry-header">
	
	<li class="author">By&nbsp;Robert McMillan and Cade Metz&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>

	<li class="entryDate"><time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2013-11-25T06:30:09+00:00">11.25.13</time>&nbsp;&nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
	<li class="entryTime">6:30 am&nbsp;&nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>

