            <li class="pinterest-small">
            <a href="//www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2013%2F11%2Fbitcoin-survival-guide%2F&media=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimages_blogs%2Fwiredenterprise%2F2013%2F11%2Fbitcoin-illo.jpg&description=Bitcoin Survival Guide: Everything You Need to Know About the Future of Money" data-pin-do="buttonPin" data-pin-config="beside" target="_blank">
